data.description: This beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath home is nestled on a 1/2 acre lot in the Million Dollar Lake Area. Upon entry, you are greeted by a two-story dining room and a living room boasting coffered ceilings. Entertain guests in the spacious living areas, adorned with natural light that filters through the large floor to ceiling windows, casting a warm and welcoming ambiance. The main level features three generously sized bedrooms and two bathrooms. The lower level has a Rec room, an additional bedroom, study, and full bathroom. Enjoy the tranquil sounds of nature on the private back deck, overlooking an expansive fenced-in back yard. Priced at an attractive $325,000, this home offers the perfect blend of value, comfort, and luxury.
